# Worker ↔ customer parity

When editing matched paths under `apps/worker-app/` and `apps/customer-app/`:

- Keep parallel file names (`httpClient.ts`, `appText.ts`, `screen-names.ts`, context/hook pairs).
- Mirror foundational changes in both apps in the same PR unless the task is role-specific UI only.
- After API type changes: update types → mappers/actions → UI; remove dead fields and mappers.

Checklist: `docs/architecture/parity-rules.md`  
Sync tracker: `docs/mono-sync-plan.md`
